## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-103"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>不同於<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>，資料會儲存於作業系統中的實體檔案而不是伺服器上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-103">An <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> differs from an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile> in that the data is stored on the server instead of in a physical file in the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-104">它也可以是讀寫物件不同於<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>，這一律是唯讀的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-104">It can also be a read-write object, unlike an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleBFile>, which is always read-only.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-105"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>可能是下列其中一種<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleType>資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-105">An <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> may be one of these <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleType> data types.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="b14aa-106">OracleType 資料類型</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-106">OracleType data type</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="b14aa-107">描述</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-107">Description</span></span>|  
|--------------------------|-----------------|  
|`Blob`|<span data-ttu-id="b14aa-108">Oracle`BLOB`包含最大值 4 gb 之二進位資料的資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-108">An Oracle `BLOB` data type that contains binary data with a maximum size of 4 gigabytes (GB).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-109">這會對應到<xref:System.Array>型別的<xref:System.Byte>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-109">This maps to an <xref:System.Array> of type <xref:System.Byte>.</span></span>|  
|`Clob`|<span data-ttu-id="b14aa-110">Oracle`CLOB`設定在伺服器上，最大值 4 gb 的資料類型包含字元資料，根據預設字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-110">An Oracle `CLOB` data type that contains character data, based on the default character set on the server, with a maximum size of 4 GB.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-111">這會對應到<xref:System.String>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-111">This maps to <xref:System.String>.</span></span>|  
|`NClob`|<span data-ttu-id="b14aa-112">Oracle`NCLOB`包含字元資料的資料型別會根據最大值 4 GB 的伺服器上的國家字元集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-112">An Oracle `NCLOB` data type that contains character data, based on the national character set on the server with a maximum size of 4 GB.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-113">這會對應到<xref:System.String>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-113">This maps to <xref:System.String>.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-114">.NET 應用程式開發人員可以擷取 Oracle`LOB`值為基本的.NET 資料類型，例如<xref:System.Array>型別的<xref:System.Byte>和<xref:System.String>，或特殊<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-114">A .NET application developer can retrieve the Oracle `LOB` values into basic .NET data types, such as <xref:System.Array> of type <xref:System.Byte> and <xref:System.String>, or the specialized <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> data type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-115"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>類別支援讀取資料來源和 Oracle 寫入`LOB`Oracle 資料庫中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-115">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> class supports reading data from and writing to the Oracle `LOB` in the Oracle database.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-116">以下是主要特性<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>區別基本的.NET 資料類型的資料類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-116">The following are the main characteristics of an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> data type that distinguish it from basic .NET data types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-117">擷取 Oracle 之後`LOB`值從 Oracle 資料庫<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>類別，您可以變更`LOB`開啟的交易和您的變更中的資料會直接反映至資料庫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-117">After you retrieve the Oracle `LOB` value from the Oracle database into the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> class, you can change the `LOB` data in an open transaction and your changes are directly reflected to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-118">如果您擷取 Oracle`LOB`值放入<xref:System.Array>型別的<xref:System.Byte>或<xref:System.String>及更新這些陣列中，您的變更不會反映到資料庫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-118">If you retrieve the Oracle `LOB` value into an <xref:System.Array> of type <xref:System.Byte> or <xref:System.String> and update these arrays, your changes are not reflected to the database.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-119">當您使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>類別來存取的區塊`LOB`值，只有該區塊會傳遞從 Oracle 資料庫給用戶端。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-119">When you use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> class to access a chunk of a `LOB` value, only that chunk is passed from the Oracle database to the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-120">當您使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetChars%2A>方法來存取的區塊`LOB`值，該值的整個內容會從 Oracle 資料庫給用戶端。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-120">When you use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetChars%2A> method to access a chunk of a `LOB` value, the entire contents of the value are passed from the Oracle database to the client.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-121">若要取得<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>物件，呼叫<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOracleLob%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-121">To obtain an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> object, call the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOracleLob%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b14aa-122">您可以建構<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob>這是 NULL，使用下列格式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b14aa-122">You can construct an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleLob> that is NULL using this format:</span></span>  
  
